tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FinancialData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  revenue DECIMAL,
  expenses DECIMAL,
  profit DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR,
  revenue DECIMAL,
  expenses DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR,
  profitability DECIMAL,
  debt_ratio DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE forecasts (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR,
  forecasted_revenue DECIMAL,
  forecasted_expenses DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE market_trends (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR,
  trading_volume DECIMAL,
  stock_price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR(100),
  revenue DECIMAL,
  expenses DECIMAL,
  profit DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE financial_ratios (
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR(100),
  roi DECIMAL,
  roe DECIMAL,
  roa DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE forecast_data (
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR(100),
  forecasted_revenue DECIMAL,
  forecasted_expenses DECIMAL,
  forecasted_profit DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE financial_metrics (
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR(100),
  liquidity_ratio DECIMAL,
  profitability_ratio DECIMAL,
  leverage_ratio DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
  date DATE,
  company_name VARCHAR(100),
  stock_price DECIMAL,
  market_cap DECIMAL,
  eps DECIMAL
);
